Gezogener Aluminium Pfeilschaft mit engen Tolleranzen und guten Flugeigenschaften. Bushings sind bereits werkseitig vormontiert.
Gewickelter Hochleistungs-Composit Pfeilschaft für Breitensportler und Bögen bis 40 Pfund Zuggewicht.
Gewickelter Composit-Carbon-Hybrid-Pfeilschaft für optimale Haltbarkeit und Treffsicherheit. Ideal für Parcour mit flacher und schneller Flugbahn.
Gewickelter Vollcarbon-Pfeilschaft mit Ultraleicht-Konzept für messerscharfe Flugbahnen und hervorragende Penetrationskraft im Ziel. Kompatibel mit den meisten 5/16″ bzw. 9/32″ Komponenten.
Der ORYX™ ist ein Multitalent für Ziel- und 3D-Schiessen. Hohe Treffsicherheit bei jeder Witterung und extreme Robustheit.
Gewickelter Vollcarbon-Pfeilschaft mit erstaunlichen Gewichtseinsparungen bei zugleich erhöhter Stabilität und Haltbarkeit. Ideal für Recurve- und Compoundschützen.

Ambition is a shaft that over the years has enjoyed considerable success and a wide audience of admirers in various fields of use from target shooting to 3D. The shaft comes complete with nock, pin and uninstalled tip, to be cut to the required size and then glued. The wide availability of pins and components, typical of top level arrows, make it the ideal shaft for first competitions and for those looking for an excellent product at an unbeatable price.

Carbon shaft with an inner diameter of 4.2mm in a bamboo look. Very beautiful and elegant, supplied with nock collar and with straightness of +/- 0.003". Robust shaft with a traditional look for the 3D field.

Sturdy and fast 32" carbon shaft with camo design (straightness 0.003 "), dedicated to hunting. Available with spine of 400 and 500 with internal diameter of 6.2 mm. Excellent value, available as a shaft or arrow.

Good quality carbon shaft recommended for universal use. Available both as an unfletched shaft and as a fletched arrow with plastic or natural vanes. Despite its low weight, which allows it to achieve a very good velocity, its a very sturdy shaft. Available with spine from 400 to 800, with an internal diameter of 6.2 mm and straightness of ± 0.006". Its features allow it to be used with either traditional hunting bows, bare bows or compound bows.
Shaft made of high-quality carbon available with spine from 250 to 1000 with an internal diameter of 4.2 mm, precise and robust shaft suitable for target and 3D shooting. Pin already inserted.

The Cross-X Plurima shaft is made of a high module carbon (40 tons), precise (straightness +/- 0.001") and available in spines from 350 to 800 (10 different sizes) with internal diameter of 3.2 mm.The Cross-X Plurima is a strong and precise shaft to obtain maximum performance in target shooting,suitable for both compound and olympic archers.Inside components compatible with the one of the X10

The new carbon Ambition shaft is characterized by new graphics and above all is a selected shaft (straightness is now +/- 0.003 ") to offer greater performance. The shaft is complete with nock and pin, and the tip is not installed and is designed to be cut to the necessary size and then glued. The wide availability of plugs and the internal components, proper of high level arrows make it the ideal auction for the first competitions and for those looking for an excellent product at an unbeatable price. In this particular version, this version comes with a silver colored crest, which makes it even more appealing.

The Madera is a product born for the traditional market. Reliable and robust, its the ideal choice for all those looking for a valid alternative to wooden arrows. The Madera is available as shaft with straightness +/-0.006" and as a complete arrow in a more affordable version with straightness +/-0.010".

For everyone who is looking for an excellent product at a more competitive price, Cross-X offers the Cube version of the Plurima shaft. The Plurima Cube has the same weight and spine characteristic but with straightness of +-/- 0.003". The shaft is sold in a 12 pieces pack with installed pin. Each dozen is selected and grouped by weight and spine.

Based on Plurima shaft, Cross-X offers Exentia: a product suitable for those with a more limited budget that still wants to be able to use a shaft of the highest level. The weight characteristics remain the same but in this case the straightness is +/- 0.005 ". Only available as shaft with pins for the installation of all the nock pin available on the market.

Large diameter shaft, designed for indoor archery. Its straightness (±0.001") and weight consistency guarantee maximum precision. Bare shaft without components, to be completed with point and pin adapter or bushing.

An extremely versatile shaft that, thanks to the use of a 40-ton high module carbon, offers an incredible lightness that makes it suitable for many uses, from target shooting to field shooting and also 3D. Pins included.

The Hurricane is an extremely versatile shaft, utilizing 40-ton high-modulus carbon to offer incredible lightness, making it suitable for multiple uses from target shooting to field and even 3D archery. All shafts come with insert nock 4,2 included.

Shaft made of high quality carbon available in spines from 350 to 1000 with an internal diameter of 4.2 mm. Precise and robust suitable for target shooting, field and 3D. Dedicated internal components. The Maior shaft is avaiable in three differente levels of straightness.

Shaft made of high quality carbon available in spines from 350 to 1000 with an internal diameter of 4.2 mm. Precise and robust suitable for target shooting, field and 3D. Dedicated internal components. The Maior shaft is avaiable in three differente levels of straightness: MAIOR CUBE - straightness ± 0.003", MAIOR PENTA - straightness ± 0.005", MAIOR OCTAGON - straightness ± 0.008"

The Ambition shaft that has proven over the years its own quality, now presents itself in the new Gold Edition version that, in addition to the golden finish on the back of the shaft, presents a remarkable straightness of +/- 0.001" proposing itself as a great choice for target shooting. Pin and pin nock included. Points not included!

Extremely lightweight and sturdy carbon shaft with 6.2 mm inside diameter. Available in 400 to 800 spine. Shaft ideal for target and 3D archery. Sold complete with 6.2 nocks (already installed) and inserts (not installed). Straightness: ± 0.002"

The Madera Light offers great speed thanks to its low weight and is therefore particularly suitable for 3D competitions or for all those looking for a fast and performing arrow. The Madera Light is available as a shaft with +/-0.003" straightness or as a +/- 0.010" straightness arrow. The shaft comes with inserted nock and loose insert.

Light, Fast and yet stable carbon shaft. Ideal for 3D shooting thanks to the 5.2mm internal diameter. The Penta version with a straightness of ±0.005" is the entry level of the Avatar family. The ideal shaft for all those looking for a thin shaft without going to OD 4.2mm. The Avatar is also appreciated for its excellent flight characteristics and a very flat trajectory. A quality shaft at a competitive price.

Version of the Avatar CUBE with cresting, very beautiful and elegant. Light, Fast and yet stable carbon shaft. Ideal for 3D shooting thanks to the 5.2mm internal diameter. The Cube version with 0.003" straightness is the best of the Avatar family. The ideal shaft for all those looking for a thin shaft without going to OD 4.2mm. The Avatar is also appreciated for its excellent flight characteristics and a very flat trajectory. A quality shaft at a competitive price.

Large diameter shaft, designed for indoor archery. Its straightness (+/- 0.008") and weight consistency guarantee good precision at an affordable price. Bare shaft without components, to be completed with point and pin adapter or bushing.

Light, Fast and yet stable carbon shaft. Ideal for 3D shooting thanks to the 5.2mm internal diameter. The Cube version with 0.003" straightness is the best of the Avatar family. The ideal shaft for all those looking for a thin shaft without going to OD 4.2mm. The Avatar is also appreciated for its excellent flight characteristics and a very flat trajectory. A quality shaft at a competitive price.
A very versatile shaft, suitable for target and 3D range. The Pegasus is light and very robust and available in 3 gradations of straightness. Shaft with straightness +/- 0.003". Complete with pin.

High-quality carbon shaft with an inner diameter of 4.2 mm. Due to the inner diameter, it is a small diameter shaft for which a variety of compatible components are available on the market. The weight is low so that the arrow can reach higher speeds and has a tight parabola. The Pegasus is recommended for target shooting, especially 3D shooting, thanks to its lightness, precision and robustness.
Lightweight and strong carbon rod with an internal diameter of 6.2mm. Available in spine from 400 to 800. Shaft suitable for target and 3D shooting.

Extremely versatile shaft suitable for multiple uses from Target to 3D shooting. Light and strong, the CUBE version has straightness 0.003" and with decorated cresting in the rear part of the shaft, giving the shaft a better look by improving also the visibility on the target.

3K carbon shaft which guarantees superior strength and an incomparable carbon look. Available as shaft or complete arrow. Straightness +/- 0.006". The shaft is complete with 6.2 nock and unglued insert.

A very robust shaft with a 5.2mm internal diameter and a straightness of 0.006" oriented for approach shooting or 3D courses. Total shaft length for all sizes is 31". Shaft complete with inserted 5.2 nock.
Inexpensive shaft with internal diameter of 6,2 mm and straightness of ±0.010, ideal for both compound and traditional bows. Includes nocks (inserted) and inserts (not inserted).

The Cross-X Iridium shaft has the same construction as the Cross-X Element shaft (full carbon), but thanks to the bright colours of the crest it is immediately recognisable. The Iridium shaft is supplied with a 4,2 mm insert nock. Straightness : ± 0.006"

The Fulmen XXL shaft has a dual purpose, suitable for both Indoor and 3D shooting. This shaft is characterized by an internal diameter of 8.0 mm and a generous outer diameter of about 9 mm (variable depending on spines), making it suitable for capturing some line points, but above all, it is an extremely lightweight shaft that is particularly suitable for 3D shooting at unknown distances. Straightness +/- 0.002". Available in a range of spines from 250 to 500 and comes with a 6.2 mm nock bushing.

Light, Fast and yet stable carbon shaft. Ideal for 3D shooting thanks to the 5.2mm internal diameter. The Penta version with a straightness of ±0.008" is the entry level of the Avatar family. The ideal shaft for all those looking for a thin shaft without going to OD 4.2mm. The Avatar is also appreciated for its excellent flight characteristics and a very flat trajectory. A quality shaft at a competitive price.

The Fulmen XXL Penta shaft has a dual purpose, on the one hand indoor shooting and on the other hand 3D shooting. This shaft is distinguished by an inner diameter of 8.0 mm and a generous outer diameter of approx. 9 mm (which varies depending on the spines), making it suitable for gaining a few line points, but above all it is an extremely light shaft which makes it particularly suitable for 3D shooting at unknown distances. Straightness +/- 0.005’.

Asta in carbonio di alta qualità, di diametro interno 4.2 mm. Il diametro interno la classifica come asta di diametro sottile, e per questa misura sono disponibili sul mercato numerosissimi componenti compatibili. Il peso è contenuto e permette quindi alla freccia di raggiungere maggiori velocità e di avere una parabola tesa. La Pegasus è consigliata per il tiro targa, e soprattutto per il tiro 3D, grazie alla sua leggerezza, precisione e robustezza. Rettilineità ±0.003".

Unique on the market for its characteristics, the new Fulmen XL is the right choice for 3D compound shooters, for all categories of barebow archery and for compound bows with limited draw lengths and poundage. A shaft with an internal diameter of 7.6 that can be used with either glue-in or screw-in points (not included), super unibushing already installed.

Schneller, leichter Premium Universal Carbonschaft für den Wettkampfschützen in Multilayer Wickeltechnik (60-90 Grad). Der Schaft ist realisiert einen superschnellen Pfeilflug mit höchster Präzision im Rundlauf und einem optimalen Schaftgewicht (Grain/Inch).
Premium Universal Carbonshaft – nicht nur für das traditionelle Bogenschießen. In Edel 3 K Carbon mit hohem Pressdruck gefertigt. Extra robust gebaut und mit Schutzlack überzogen.

Edel Carbonschaft mit Rindenholz Optik der extrem schwer-robust gebaut ist. Universal Carbon Schaft für das traditionelles Bogenschießen speziell auch für für Bogen die gerne etwas mehr an Pfeilgewicht benötigen!
Premium Universal Carbonschaft für das traditionelle Bogenschießen aus kreuzgewickeltem Carbon (6 Layer). Wunderschöner Schaft mit Zedernholz Maserung (Rinden-Optik).
Universal Carbon Schaft für das traditionelle Bogenschießen speziell für Bogen die etwas mehr an Pfeilgewicht benötigen!
Dünner Carbonschaft ID 0.166 inch / 4.20 mm, extrem stabil, in schöner, dunkler Holzoptik. Jeder Schaft ist ein Unikat.
Premium Universal Carbonschaft für das traditionelle Bogenschießen in Edel-Carbon mit Rindenholz-Optik.

Premium Universal Carbonschaft für das Bogenschießen (Halle und Outdoor) in Edel-Carbon, 3-K Optik. Ideal für die Halle, aber auch im Außenbereich geeignet für 3D Sport, Lammelscheiben und Stramitscheiben, sehr robust unter den 9 mm Schäften!

Premium Universal Carbonschaft für das Fita, Feld, Wald, Compound, 3D Bogenschießen in Edel-Carbon, Sicht Optik. Enorm stabil. Der Schaft ist aus 100 % Carbon in Kreuzwickeltechnik hergestellt, realisiert einen super schnellen Pfeilflug mit höchster Präzision im Rundlauf, und einem optimalen Schaft Gewicht an Grain/Inch.
Premium Universal Carbonschaft (linear, plain Sicht-Optik) mit höchster Performance und 5,2 mm Innendurchmesser.

Premium Universal linear two sides, Carbon Schaft, Linear Gewebe, with a nice white print. The newly developed Nijora Ilyan-pro Premium Edition carbon shaft has a special 3K cross winding 90-60 consisting of 8 layers of carbon fabric. The construction of the shaft is naturally designed for all types of bows.

Premium Universal Carbon Schaft für das Bogenschießen Recurve, Compound, Halle, und Atlatl. Höchste Präzision im Rundlauf, realisiert einen super schnellen Pfeilflug und einem optimalen Schaft Gewicht an Grain/Inch.

Universal Carbonschaft für den gesamten Bogensport – 3D, Fita, Feld/Wald. Der Schaft ist aus 100% Carbon in Kreuzwickeltechnik hergestellt. Der Innendurchmesser ist die Normgröße 0,245 Zoll / 6,20 mm – dadurch passen die auf dem Markt am meisten benötigten und verfügbaren 5/16″ bzw. 9/32″ Komponenten (Spitzen, Inserts und Nocken).

Premium Universal linear two sides, Carbonshaft, 3K / Twill Gewebe, mit schönem bunten orange gehaltenem 4 Farben Druck. Der neu entwickelte Nijora Linawa (starker Büffel) 33 inch Premium Edition Carbonschaft hat eine spezielle 3K Kreuz Wicklung 90-60 bestehend aus 8 lagigem Carbon Layer Geweben.
Premium Universal konical Carbon Schaft, Sicht Optik mit Schutzlack, höchste Performance.

Premium Universal linear two sides, Carbon Schaft, 3 K / Twill Gewebe, mit schönem bunten 4 Farben Druck. Der neu entwickelte Nijora Yona Premium Edition Carbonschaft hat eine spezielle 3 K Kreuz Wicklung 90-60 bestehend aus 8 lagigen Carbon Layer Geweben.
Universal Carbon Schaft für den gesamten Bogensport (Fita, Feld/Wald, 3D). Extrem stabiler Schaft für Anfänger und Fortgeschrittene.
Premium High Class Carbonschaft in 10 Layer light weight MS Carbon. Der Onawa Pro X aus 100 % Carbon ist in Kreuzwickeltechnik hergestellt.
Premium High Class Carbonschaft aus 10 Layer light weight MS Carbon in Kreuzwickeltechnik. Neuestes Weltmarkt Carbon mit 40 Tonnen Wickel-Pressdruck.
Premium High Class Carbonschaft aus 10 Layer light weight MS Carbon in Kreuzwickeltechnik. Neuestes Weltmarkt Carbon mit 40 Tonnen Wickel-Pressdruck.

Universal Carbon Schaft für das traditionelle Bogenschießen. Der dünne 100 % Carbon Schaft ist in Kreuzwickeltechnik hergestellt. Er hat einen Außendurchmesser von 5,30 mm bis max. 6.02 mm je nach Spinewert. Der Innendurchmesser ist die Normgröße 0,166 Zoll = 4,22 mm. Dadurch passen die auf dem Markt am meisten benötigten und verfügbaren 4,22 mm Komponenten.

Premium Universal Carbon Schaft für das traditionelle Bogenschießen in Edel-Carbon, Sichtoptik mit Schutzlack, höchste Performance. Sehr robust gebaut – etwas mehr Gewicht als ein Standardschaft. Somit ideal für Bogen die etwas mehr an Pfeilgewicht benötigen.

Premium Universal Carbonschaft für das Bogenschießen mit dem Compound, Blankbogen und anderen Bögen, die leichte Schäfte mögen. Enorm stabiler Schaft aus Edel-Carbon mit geringen Gewichtstoleranzen: max. 2 grain bei 12 Schäften.
Extrem stabiler, preiswerter Schaft, ideal für den Anfänger und Hobbybogensportler.

Premium Universal conical / tapered Carbonshaft with special winding, thinner at nock end than insert side. Features dual lacquering with white 2K lacquer at front and wood grain decor. Optimized for flat trajectory and precision.

Premium Universal conical/tapered Carbonschaft, Sicht-Optik, höchste Performance. Der Nijora Taperon Crust Carbonschaft hat eine Spezialwicklung – er ist am Nockende dünner als an der Insert-Seite. Innen ist er jedoch linear 0.245 inch / 6,20 mm. Das ist somit eine getaperte, konische Form.

Der Nijora Taperon SX (Pro) Carbon Schaft hat eine spezielle konische Wicklung, er ist am Nockende und and der Spitze dünner, als in der Mitte. Durch diesen neu entwickelten Aufbau mit spezial Carbonfasern stabilisiert der Taperon SX (Pro) Schaft schneller. Dadurch hat er eine noch flachere Flugbahn gegenüber einem normalem zylindrischen Schaft mit gleichen Gewichts und Spine Werten.

Premium Universal conical Carbonschaft mit Sicht-Optik und höchster Performance. Durch spezielle konische Wicklung stabilisiert der Taperon Schaft schneller und hat dadurch eine noch flachere Flugbahn.
Premium Universal Carbon Schaft für das traditionelle Bogenschießen in 3 k Edel-Carbon, Sicht Optik, bzw. mit dunkler Holz Sicht Optik.

Der Tokala M Carbonschaft ist beschichtet mit einer Micron Schutzschicht: feine Silizium Kristalle schließen die feine Carbonstruktur von den Carbon Layern und härten aus. Dadurch ergibt sich eine glattere und härtere Oberfläche des Carbonschafts.
Premium Universal Carbonschaft für traditionelles Bogenschießen, Compound und Fita mit superschnellem Pfeilflug und höchster Präzision.

Premium Universal linear two sides, Carbon Schaft, plain Sicht Optik, mit schönem bunt Druck für höchste Performance. Der neu entwickelte Nijora Zitkala Carbon Schaft hat eine spezielle Linear Wicklung bestehend aus 8 lagigem Carbon Layer Geweben.

Fat arrow shaft with 0.315” Inner Diameter, World Archery Maximum Compliant Diameter carbon arrow for compound shooters, ideal for indoor compound competition.

The ALPHA X is built with 100% carbon construction in standard-diameter with 0.006” straightness, which makes it has the accuracy and extreme durability, it’s ideal for compound bow or tradition bow for target shooting practice or hunting!

CA320 is an evolutional version of ELITE XT designed for Olympic target shooting, spindled shape based on CAC construction Offering the competitive shooter exceptional speed and accuracy with little worry of wind drift, it’s almost an unfair advantage compare with any other pure carbon arrows, taper tail providing the incredible clearance and release forgiveness, it can provide the strong and stable output, it’s the ulitmate arrow for Long distance targeting shoot.

Parallel shaped CAC structure arrows, Alloy core covered by high modules carbon fiber make the shaft more durable and easier tuning, the CAC construction can greatly reduces ineffective twisting and maintains an excellent attitude during flight, super slim shaft maximum speed and accuracy with extremely less wind deflection, that is a true all-round performer for Indoor or outdoor target shooting, recommended for compound bow.

CA320 PRO is designed for Compound bow target shooting specially, taper front design based on CAC construction Offering the competitive shooter exceptional speed and accuracy with little worry of wind drift, parallel tail enhances the durability with compound bow, it can provide the strong and stable output, it’s a true all-round performer for compound bow target shoot at any range!

Entry-level ACA arrow, suitable for all types of archery shooting, whether long distance or shorter distance, recurve bow or compound bow. The CAC construction greatly reduces ineffective twisting and maintains an excellent attitude during flight.

The ICEPOINT 100% high modual carbon arrow was designed for long-range target accuracy, super slim shaft maximum speed and accuracy with extremely less wind deflection. The high modual carbon is customized specially, fully considered the GPI and also the balance between rigidity & toughness of the shaft, which make the arrow has unmatched durability and straightness retention.

The PRECISION is built with 100% carbon construction in standard-diameter, light weight design selectively engineered to maximize speed and flatten trajectory, every arrow is digitally spine aligned and Straightness tolerances are held to a standard of .003 for increased accuracy and each shoot consistency, it’s ideal for Field, target and 3D shooting.

The ALPHA XT is an economical arrow, built with 100% carbon construction in Micro-diameter, which keeps it durable and more wind resistant for long-range accuracy, making it optimal for Entry-level/Youth archers target shooting as well as recreational use, the low spine with special adapter also great for hunting.

Renowned as the arrow of choice for Olympic champions, the X10 sets the standard for precision and quality in archery. The new Parallel Pro carries this legacy forward as a lightweight, easy-tuning 4mm shaft crafted with the highest tolerances and high-modulus carbon fiber.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The X10 is Easton's flagship target arrow, featuring a high-performance carbon construction with a micro-diameter design for reduced wind drift and improved accuracy. Used by elite archers worldwide.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. High-performance target arrow with micro-diameter design for reduced wind drift and enhanced accuracy. Features high-strength carbon construction and precision tolerances for competitive shooting.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The Superdrive Micro features a micro-diameter design for reduced wind drift and increased penetration, with high-strength carbon construction for durability and performance in hunting applications.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The Superdrive 23 is a high-performance hunting arrow featuring Easton's 4D Technology for superior accuracy and penetration. The 23 refers to the 0.246-inch outer diameter, optimized for deep penetration while maintaining excellent flight characteristics.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The Superdrive 25 is a high-performance hunting arrow featuring Easton's patented Superdrive technology for improved accuracy and penetration. It has a micro-diameter design for reduced wind drift and increased speed.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The Superdrive 27 is a high-performance hunting arrow featuring Easton's advanced carbon construction for durability and precision. Designed for speed and accuracy, it offers consistent spine alignment and tight tolerances.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The 4Mm Axis Pro is a high-performance hunting arrow featuring a micro-diameter design for improved speed and penetration. It utilizes Easton's Advanced Bonding Technology for durability and straightness.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The 4Mm Axis arrows from Easton Archery are designed for hunting, featuring a durable carbon construction with high straightness and weight tolerances for consistent performance.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. High-performance target arrow with 4mm micro-diameter design for reduced wind drift and improved accuracy. Features Match Grade construction for consistent spine alignment and weight distribution.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The 4MM FMJ features a full metal jacket design with a carbon core for durability and penetration. It combines the weight-forward momentum of a traditional FMJ with the speed of a 4mm diameter shaft.
Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. High-performance target arrow with Full Metal Jacket (FMJ) technology for maximum durability and consistency.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The 5MM FMJ features a full metal jacket design with a carbon core for maximum penetration and durability. The arrow is designed for hunting with high weight-forward balance and extreme straightness.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The 5mm FMJ Match Grade arrows feature a full metal jacket design for maximum durability and consistency. The high-carbon construction provides excellent stiffness-to-weight ratio for competitive target shooting.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The Easton 5Mm Axis is a high-performance hunting arrow featuring a micro-diameter design for improved accuracy and penetration. It utilizes Easton's Advanced Tubing Technology for durability and consistency.
Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. High-performance target arrow with match-grade consistency, designed for competitive archery with exceptional straightness and weight tolerances.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The 5MM FMJ 5MM Axis is a high-performance hunting arrow featuring a carbon core with a metal jacket for durability and penetration. It offers excellent weight-forward balance and straightness for precision shooting.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The 6.5mm Axis arrows feature a micro-diameter design for reduced wind drift and increased penetration. Built with high-modulus carbon for durability and precision, they are optimized for hunting applications.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. High-performance target arrow with 6.5mm diameter for reduced wind drift and improved accuracy. Features Match Grade construction for exceptional consistency.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The 6.5mm FMJ features a full metal jacket design with a carbon core for durability and penetration. The aluminum jacket provides strength while maintaining a slim diameter for reduced wind drift.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The 6.5mm FMJ Match Grade arrow features a carbon outer layer with an aluminum core for superior stiffness and durability. Designed for competitive target archery, it offers exceptional straightness and consistency.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The Bloodline arrow features a high-strength carbon construction with a micro-diameter design for deep penetration and accuracy. It includes a reinforced nock collar for durability and is optimized for hunting applications.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The Deep Six arrow features a micro-diameter design for superior penetration and accuracy, with a high-strength carbon construction for durability in hunting applications.
Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The X7 Eclipse is a high-performance target arrow featuring a durable aluminum-carbon composite construction for consistent accuracy and tight groupings.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The X27 is a high-performance hunting arrow featuring Easton's patented Carbon Core Technology for durability and precision. Designed for maximum penetration and accuracy in hunting scenarios.

arrows.description: Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The Rx7 is designed for indoor recurve archery, featuring ultra-tight tolerances and a micro-diameter design for superior accuracy and consistency.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The Easton A/C/E is a high-performance target arrow featuring 100% carbon construction, exceptional straightness, and tight weight tolerances for competitive archery.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The Avance Sport is a high-performance target arrow designed for competitive archers. It features a micro-diameter carbon construction for speed and accuracy, with consistent spine alignment and weight distribution.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The XX75 Jazz is a durable and affordable aluminum target arrow, known for its consistent performance and straightness. It features a smooth finish and is designed for target archery.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The Venture is a durable and affordable carbon hunting arrow designed for reliability and performance. Features a precision straightness tolerance and consistent weight for accurate shooting.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The Vector Arrow is designed for hunters seeking a balance of speed and accuracy. Features a micro-diameter design for reduced wind drift and enhanced penetration.

The Gold Tip X-Cutter Pro is the most popular shaft in 3D archery, look to the winner's podium and you'll see why. Large diameter and lightweight construction give it an almost unfair advantage. Components are sold separately.
Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. High-performance target arrows designed for competitive archery, featuring precision straightness and weight consistency.
Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. High-performance target arrows with reinforced nock end for durability and consistent flight. Designed for competitive archery.
Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. High-performance target arrow with precision straightness and weight tolerances, designed for competitive archery.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. High-performance target arrow with micro-diameter design for reduced wind drift and improved accuracy. Features reinforced nock end for durability and consistent performance.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The X-Cutter Plus target arrows feature a high-performance carbon construction with precision straightness and weight tolerances. Designed for competitive target archery, they offer consistent flight and durability.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The Gold Tip Triple-X Plus Target Arrows are designed for competitive target archery, featuring high-strength carbon construction, tight straightness tolerances, and consistent weight distribution for optimal accuracy.

Technical data from DeepSeek knowledge base. The GT 30X Plus is a high-performance target arrow designed for competitive archers. It features a micro-diameter design for reduced wind drift and improved accuracy, with a reinforced core for durability and consistent performance.

schema:
CREATE TABLE component_categories (
            id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
            name TEXT UNIQUE NOT NULL,
            description TEXT,
            specifications_schema TEXT,  -- JSON schema for this category
            created_at TEXT DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
        )

CREATE TABLE components (
            id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
            category_id INTEGER NOT NULL,
            manufacturer TEXT NOT NULL,
            model_name TEXT NOT NULL,
            specifications TEXT,  -- JSON field for type-specific specs
            compatibility_rules TEXT,  -- JSON field for compatibility logic
            image_url TEXT,
            local_image_path TEXT,
            price_range TEXT,
            description TEXT,
            source_url TEXT,
            scraped_at TEXT,
            created_at TEXT DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
            FOREIGN KEY (category_id) REFERENCES component_categories (id),
            UNIQUE(manufacturer, model_name, category_id)
        )

CREATE TABLE arrow_component_compatibility (
            id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
            arrow_id INTEGER NOT NULL,
            component_id INTEGER NOT NULL,
            compatibility_type TEXT CHECK(compatibility_type IN ('direct', 'universal', 'adapter_required', 'incompatible')),
            compatibility_score REAL DEFAULT 0.0,  -- 0.0 to 1.0
            notes TEXT,
            verified BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
            verified_by TEXT,  -- User ID who verified
            created_at TEXT DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
            FOREIGN KEY (arrow_id) REFERENCES arrows (id),
            FOREIGN KEY (component_id) REFERENCES components (id),
            UNIQUE(arrow_id, component_id)
        )

CREATE TABLE compatibility_rules (
            id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
            category_name TEXT NOT NULL,
            rule_name TEXT NOT NULL,
            rule_logic TEXT NOT NULL,  -- JSON field with matching logic
            priority INTEGER DEFAULT 1,
            active BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE,
            description TEXT,
            created_at TEXT DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
        )

CREATE TABLE arrows (
            id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
            manufacturer TEXT NOT NULL,
            model_name TEXT NOT NULL,
            material TEXT,
            carbon_content TEXT,
            arrow_type TEXT,  -- target, hunting, etc.
            description TEXT,
            image_url TEXT,
            source_url TEXT,
            scraped_at TEXT,
            created_at TEXT DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, retailer_data TEXT DEFAULT NULL,
            UNIQUE(manufacturer, model_name)
        )

CREATE TABLE spine_specifications (
            id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
            arrow_id INTEGER NOT NULL,
            spine INTEGER NOT NULL,
            outer_diameter REAL,
            gpi_weight REAL NOT NULL,
            inner_diameter REAL,
            diameter_category TEXT,  -- Categorized diameter classification
            length_options TEXT,  -- JSON array of available lengths
            wall_thickness REAL,
            insert_weight_range TEXT,
            nock_size TEXT,
            notes TEXT,
            straightness_tolerance TEXT,
            weight_tolerance TEXT,
            created_at TEXT DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
            FOREIGN KEY (arrow_id) REFERENCES arrows (id),
            UNIQUE(arrow_id, spine)
        )

CREATE TABLE users (
            id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
            google_id TEXT UNIQUE NOT NULL,
            email TEXT UNIQUE NOT NULL,
            name TEXT,
            profile_picture_url TEXT,
            created_at TEXT DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
        )

CREATE TABLE bow_setups (
            id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
            user_id INTEGER NOT NULL,
            name TEXT NOT NULL,
            bow_type TEXT NOT NULL,
            draw_weight REAL NOT NULL,
            draw_length REAL NOT NULL,
            arrow_length REAL NOT NULL,
            point_weight REAL NOT NULL,
            nock_weight REAL,
            fletching_weight REAL,
            insert_weight REAL,
            created_at TEXT DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
            FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users (id)
        )

CREATE TABLE retailer_sources (
                id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
                retailer_name TEXT NOT NULL,
                base_url TEXT NOT NULL,
                language TEXT DEFAULT 'en',
                currency TEXT DEFAULT 'USD',
                scraping_config TEXT,  -- JSON config for scraping
                created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
                updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
                UNIQUE(retailer_name, base_url)
            )

CREATE TABLE retailer_arrow_data (
                id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
                arrow_id INTEGER NOT NULL,
                retailer_id INTEGER NOT NULL,
                source_url TEXT NOT NULL,
                
                -- Pricing and availability
                price REAL,
                currency TEXT DEFAULT 'USD',
                stock_quantity INTEGER,
                availability_status TEXT,
                
                -- Enhanced specifications
                straightness_tolerance TEXT,
                weight_tolerance TEXT,
                additional_specs TEXT,  -- JSON for extra specs
                
                -- Performance data
                recommended_bow_types TEXT,  -- JSON array
                intended_uses TEXT,          -- JSON array
                performance_notes TEXT,      -- JSON array
                technical_notes TEXT,        -- JSON array
                
                -- Images and description
                retailer_images TEXT,        -- JSON array of image URLs
                product_description TEXT,
                
                -- Metadata
                scraped_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
                updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
                
                FOREIGN KEY (arrow_id) REFERENCES arrows (id),
                FOREIGN KEY (retailer_id) REFERENCES retailer_sources (id),
                UNIQUE(arrow_id, retailer_id)
            )

CREATE TABLE arrow_enhancements (
                id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
                arrow_id INTEGER NOT NULL,
                
                -- Enhanced technical specs
                insert_compatibility TEXT,    -- Compatible insert types/weights
                nock_compatibility TEXT,      -- Compatible nock types
                point_compatibility TEXT,     -- Compatible point weights/types
                
                -- Performance characteristics
                penetration_rating INTEGER,  -- 1-10 scale
                accuracy_rating INTEGER,     -- 1-10 scale  
                durability_rating INTEGER,   -- 1-10 scale
                flight_characteristics TEXT, -- JSON with flight data
                
                -- Real-world data
                user_reviews_summary TEXT,   -- Summary of user feedback
                expert_recommendations TEXT, -- Expert opinions
                competition_usage TEXT,      -- Competition/tournament usage
                
                -- Testing data
                test_results TEXT,           -- JSON with test data
                ballistic_coefficient REAL,
                wind_resistance_rating INTEGER,
                
                created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
                updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
                
                FOREIGN KEY (arrow_id) REFERENCES arrows (id),
                UNIQUE(arrow_id)
            )

CREATE TABLE price_history (
                id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
                arrow_id INTEGER NOT NULL,
                retailer_id INTEGER NOT NULL,
                price REAL NOT NULL,
                currency TEXT NOT NULL,
                stock_quantity INTEGER,
                availability_status TEXT,
                recorded_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
                
                FOREIGN KEY (arrow_id) REFERENCES arrows (id),
                FOREIGN KEY (retailer_id) REFERENCES retailer_sources (id)
            )
